      "comment": "STEELY DAWN (7) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only a neck (20.15) behind Wilgunya Prince at this track. Top chance in this line up. OPHIDIAN (2) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 0.8 lengths third (20.18) over 350m at this track and making it two placings on end. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Expecting another good run. SHE LIES EASY (8) stuck on well last time to finish half a length back in second (17.00) at Casino in a Grade 5 over 300m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Bold showing expected. EXONERATE (1) is worth including.",
